data.description: Welcome to your new Wedgewood Home tucked away in the highly sought after Greenfield Estates of Logandale. This beautifully appointed residence provides spacious living starting with generously sized living areas & bedrooms, all accentuated by hand selected fixtures & finishes. Enjoy sumptuous diamond patterned carpet adding a dash of luxury into your lifestyle. Indulge in the ultimate comfort of a downstairs primary suite, complete with an on-suite offering dual vanities & a massive soaking tub. The kitchen is a chef's dream featuring granite countertops, and island built for entertaining, & a subzero refrigerator. Step outside & live like a Rockstar with a beach entry pebble tech swimming pool perfect for those hot summer days. The private basket ball courts provide endless entertainment possibilities, while the extended driveway allows for ample guest parking & storage for all of your toys. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity - schedule your showing today!
